choices.text:
### Human:
Put together a healthy meal plan for me for today presuming no dietary restrictions.
### Assistant:

Here is your healthy meal plan for today:

Breakfast: Oatmeal with fresh fruit and honey.
Lunch: Grilled chicken breast with roasted vegetables and quinoa.
Snack: Apple slices with almond butter.
Dinner: Baked salmon with sweet potato and green beans.
Enjoy your healthy meal plan!
